{"title":"正午，挖掘者","authors":["李汉荣"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"正午，挖掘者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李汉荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他举起的锄头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在空中静止了一小会儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（与阳光面谈了一小会儿）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就深入黝黑的泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他连续挖掘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他连续划着弧线和直线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟也在天上划着弧线和直线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（每一条线都指向卑微的食物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也指向云彩和无限的领域）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他微不足道的每一个动作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"影响着下半年土地的收成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也影响了我对"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限的体验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邻近的河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄收藏了他的倒影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在水里挖掘着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更深处的水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳渐渐西斜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片云正好路过他的头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在云影里小立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起头来，他看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖先，早已站成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周的青山……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}